WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.667 --> 00:00:01.901
(laughing)

2
00:00:01.901 --> 00:00:04.003
♪ Come on in
and join the fun ♪

3
00:00:04.003 --> 00:00:06.506
-(squawks)
-♪ 'Cause our party's
just begun ♪

4
00:00:06.906 --> 00:00:09.476
♪ It's such a treat
when best friends meet ♪

5
00:00:09.476 --> 00:00:11.111
♪ We're inviting everyone ♪

6
00:00:11.111 --> 00:00:13.513
♪ So jump right in,
there's a lot to do ♪

7
00:00:13.513 --> 00:00:18.218
♪ Minnie's Bow-Toons
are waiting for you ♪

8
00:00:20.820 --> 00:00:22.822
Oh yeah! (laughs)

9
00:00:22.822 --> 00:00:24.324
Oh, girls! It's our first

10
00:00:24.324 --> 00:00:26.793
big swim on
the first day of summer!

11
00:00:26.793 --> 00:00:27.827
(laughter)

12
00:00:28.294 --> 00:00:30.230
Oh, I've been waitin' for this.

13
00:00:30.864 --> 00:00:34.100
And now,
let's make a big splash!

14
00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:35.735
(laughter)

15
00:00:35.735 --> 00:00:37.270
-(sun sizzling)
-(seagull cawing)

16
00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:39.773
♪ ♪

17
00:00:39.773 --> 00:00:41.841
(uneasy chirping)

18
00:00:41.841 --> 00:00:43.243
-(sizzle)
-(yelps)

19
00:00:43.243 --> 00:00:45.345
-Hot! Hot! Hot!
-(tires screech)

20
00:00:45.345 --> 00:00:46.946
-Oh...
-CUCKOO LOCA: Cannonball!

21
00:00:46.946 --> 00:00:48.748
-(splash)
-(laughter)

22
00:00:49.182 --> 00:00:50.417
Ah-ha!

23
00:00:50.417 --> 00:00:52.719
-Look out below!
-DAISY: Look out!

24
00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:54.020
(laughter)

25
00:00:54.020 --> 00:00:55.522
♪ ♪

26
00:00:55.522 --> 00:00:56.723
(sizzle)

27
00:00:56.723 --> 00:00:58.758
Ah! Huh? Ah...

28
00:00:58.758 --> 00:01:00.460
Ah-ha!

29
00:01:01.127 --> 00:01:03.029
Who wants a juice box?

30
00:01:03.029 --> 00:01:04.831
-(splash)
-Hey!

31
00:01:04.831 --> 00:01:05.932
A penguin?

32
00:01:05.932 --> 00:01:08.568
Oh! He's just trying
to cool off!

33
00:01:08.568 --> 00:01:11.071
It's fine! Let's get
back to our game.

34
00:01:11.071 --> 00:01:13.807
(laughter, chatter)

35
00:01:14.174 --> 00:01:16.876
-(fan blowing)
-(screaming)

36
00:01:17.377 --> 00:01:18.545
MINNIE:
Oh m-m-my!

37
00:01:18.545 --> 00:01:20.947
He's ruining our pool day!

38
00:01:21.848 --> 00:01:23.416
Now, see here, you...

39
00:01:23.416 --> 00:01:25.318
-you adorably cute penguin!
-(fan stops)

40
00:01:25.318 --> 00:01:28.188
If you want to swim with us,
you have to play nice!

41
00:01:28.188 --> 00:01:30.457
-DAISY: Marco!
-Oh! Polo!

42
00:01:30.457 --> 00:01:31.858
-(laughter)
-Hm!

43
00:01:31.858 --> 00:01:35.095
♪ ♪

44
00:01:35.095 --> 00:01:36.963
-(chair wobbles)
-(clattering)

45
00:01:36.963 --> 00:01:39.065
-(ice crackling)
-Oh m-m-my!

46
00:01:39.065 --> 00:01:40.500
Marco!

47
00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:41.868
Him again? Now, look here!

48
00:01:41.868 --> 00:01:44.337
You're welcome to stay,
but you gotta stop--

49
00:01:44.337 --> 00:01:45.405
Ah!

50
00:01:46.172 --> 00:01:47.474
-Oh my!
-Daisy!

51
00:01:47.941 --> 00:01:49.409
(both straining)

52
00:01:49.409 --> 00:01:50.443
Are you okay?

53
00:01:50.443 --> 00:01:52.846
I feel like a q-q-quack-sicle!

54
00:01:52.846 --> 00:01:54.614
♪ ♪

55
00:01:54.614 --> 00:01:56.049
(crunching)

56
00:01:56.049 --> 00:01:58.418
Woo-hoo! Ah...

57
00:01:58.418 --> 00:01:59.752
That does it!

58
00:01:59.752 --> 00:02:01.621
-(shivering)
-Time for me to break the ice.

59
00:02:02.055 --> 00:02:03.790
(creak, crank)

60
00:02:03.790 --> 00:02:04.891
(sizzle)

61
00:02:06.559 --> 00:02:07.594
Ah! Whoa!

62
00:02:08.228 --> 00:02:09.895
Hot! Hot! Aw...

63
00:02:09.895 --> 00:02:10.929
And that's that.

64
00:02:10.930 --> 00:02:13.299
♪ ♪

65
00:02:13.299 --> 00:02:14.834
(grunts) Woo!

66
00:02:14.834 --> 00:02:16.269
Tweedlyee... ah!

67
00:02:16.269 --> 00:02:18.071
Oh, it's on, penguin!

68
00:02:18.071 --> 00:02:19.339
-Nuh-uh.
-(crank)

69
00:02:19.339 --> 00:02:20.640
-Uh-huh!
-(crank)

70
00:02:20.640 --> 00:02:24.010
-(both grunting)
-(lever cranking)

71
00:02:24.010 --> 00:02:25.445
♪ ♪

72
00:02:25.445 --> 00:02:26.746
-(struggling)
-(snap)

73
00:02:27.180 --> 00:02:28.348
(clang)

74
00:02:28.348 --> 00:02:30.517
(fizzling)

75
00:02:30.517 --> 00:02:32.685
-(ice crackling)
-Oh no.

76
00:02:33.052 --> 00:02:34.420
(pop, clatter)

77
00:02:34.420 --> 00:02:36.756
(cheering, kiss)

78
00:02:37.123 --> 00:02:38.758
-(laughing)
-(bouncing)

79
00:02:38.758 --> 00:02:41.394
No more swimming... Ah!

80
00:02:41.394 --> 00:02:44.330
-No more splashing. Whoa!
-Woo!

81
00:02:44.998 --> 00:02:47.000
But, there is one thing
we can do!

82
00:02:47.934 --> 00:02:50.470
(laughter)

83
00:02:50.470 --> 00:02:52.705
(cheering)

84
00:02:52.705 --> 00:02:55.275
(laughing)

85
00:02:55.275 --> 00:02:57.443
(cheering)

86
00:02:57.443 --> 00:02:59.445
♪ ♪

